{"title":"HDU 5527 Too Rich","date":"2018-05-06T16:00:00.000Z","author":"luoyayu","excerpt":"","slug":"2018-05-07-HDU 5527 Too Rich","comments":true,"tags":["ACM-未分类"],"categories":["ACM"],"updated":"2018-08-19T04:22:30.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"题意\"><a href=\"#题意\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意\"></a>题意</h1><p>给出10张硬币，问如何凑出P￥且数量最多，无方案输出-1</p>\n<h1 id=\"思路\"><a href=\"#思路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路\"></a>思路</h1><p>如果面值连续，后一个是前一个的倍数，从大往小凑，用小因子去凑更多的硬币，<br>但是本题存在$20,200$特殊处理这两种情况100￥折成2<em>50,500拆成5</em>100，或200*2+100</p>\n<h1 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h1><iframe id=\"iFrame0\" name=\"iFrame0\" width=\"100%\" onload=\"this.height=iFrame0.document.body.scrollHeight\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"/htmlcode/hdu/hdu5527.html\"></iframe>\n\n<p>&gt;<br>  星星<br>&gt;<br>  当夜色降临<br>  我站在台阶上倾听；<br>  星星蜂拥在花园里<br>  而我站在黑暗中。<br>&gt;<br>  听，一颗星星落地作响！<br>  你别赤脚在这草地上散步，<br>  我的花园到处是星星的碎片</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"2018-08-02-hello-world"},"next":{"title":"IEE754","slug":"2018-04-02-IEEE754"},"link":"/2018/05/07","toc":[{"title":"题意","id":"题意","index":"1"},{"title":"思路","id":"思路","index":"2"},{"title":"代码","id":"代码","index":"3"}]}